      "title": "3,500 MT of LP Gas to reach SL today (21)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro Gas says that a vessel carrying 3,500 MT of LP gas is scheduled to reach the country today (21) morning.",
        "Chairman of Litro Muditha Peiris said that 60,000 cooking gas cylinders will be distributed to the provinces outside of the Colombo District today (21) and 21,000 cooking gas cylinders will be distributed to the Colombo district.",
        "The Chairman further said that steps will be taken to further increase the number of gas cylinders distributed tomorrow (22)."
      ],
